ecting birds, bats and insects at night in ways scientists did not expect]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131260426.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/how-streetlights-may-be-affecting-birds-bats-and-insects-at-night-in-ways-scientists-did-not-expect/articleshow/131260426.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/how-streetlights-may-be-affecting-birds-bats-and-insects-at-night-in-ways-scientists-did-not-expect/articleshow/131260426.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T14:32:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131260493,imgsize-1276426.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Archaeologists found an intact Anglo-Saxon burial chamber in Essex, challenging old ‘Dark Ages’ views]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131245354.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Archaeologists unearthed the Prittlewell burial, an intact chamber revealing high-status Anglo-Saxon objects. This princely grave provides a complete archaeological context for study. The well-preserved artifacts and their arrangement showcase structured elite culture and burial traditions. This discovery challenges the 'Dark Ages' interpretation, highlighting sophisticated societies with foreign trade and organized labor in early medieval England.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/archaeologists-found-an-intact-anglo-saxon-burial-chamber-in-essex-challenging-old-dark-ages-views/articleshow/131245354.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/archaeologists-found-an-intact-anglo-saxon-burial-chamber-in-essex-challenging-old-dark-ages-views/articleshow/131245354.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T16:48:48+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131245370,imgsize-1584971.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Scientists say Antarctic mud revealed a rainforest near the South Pole]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131245211.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Fossils of an intact root network, pollen, and spores discovered near the South Pole reveal a temperate rainforest existed during the Cretaceous period. This ancient ecosystem, found in a sediment core from the Amundsen Sea, indicates West Antarctica was ice-free and supported dense vegetation with an average temperature of 12 degrees Celsius.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/scientists-say-antarctic-mud-revealed-a-rainforest-near-the-south-pole/articleshow/131245211.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/scientists-say-antarctic-mud-revealed-a-rainforest-near-the-south-pole/articleshow/131245211.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T16:00:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131245222,imgsize-1984685.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[A 13-year-old built a LEGO Braille printer to make reading more affordable]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131244151.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A 13-year-old American innovator, Shubham Banerjee, revolutionized Braille printing with Braigo, a remarkably affordable device built from Lego blocks.  This invention addresses the high cost of traditional embossers, making tactile reading accessible to more visually impaired individuals.  Braigo's simple design and focus on affordability have garnered significant attention, highlighting the power of user-centric problem-solving.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/a-13-year-old-built-a-lego-braille-printer-to-make-reading-more-affordable/articleshow/131244151.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/a-13-year-old-built-a-lego-braille-printer-to-make-reading-more-affordable/articleshow/131244151.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T15:32:18+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131245053,imgsize-1076232.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Vietnamese Communist revolutionary leader Ho Chi Minh: “To reap a return in ten years, plant trees. To reap a return in 100, cultivate the people.”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131260511.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-vietnamese-communist-revolutionary-leader-ho-chi-minh-to-reap-a-return-in-ten-years-plant-trees-to-reap-a-return-in-100-cultivate-the-people-/articleshow/131260511.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-vietnamese-communist-revolutionary-leader-ho-chi-minh-to-reap-a-return-in-ten-years-plant-trees-to-reap-a-return-in-100-cultivate-the-people-/articleshow/131260511.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T15:58:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131260498,imgsize-28914.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘It’s not their fault’: Amazon UK boss says education system is failing young workers]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131260176.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/its-not-their-fault-amazon-uk-boss-says-education-system-is-failing-young-workers/articleshow/131260176.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/its-not-their-fault-amazon-uk-boss-says-education-system-is-failing-young-workers/articleshow/131260176.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T14:16:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131260279,imgsize-463361.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[In 2017, Colorado construction workers accidentally dug up a very rare dinosaur fossil]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131243140.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A construction project in Thornton, Colorado, unearthed a significant prehistoric find. Workers discovered a fossilised skeleton initially thought to be a Triceratops. Further examination revealed it was a much rarer Torosaurus. This discovery, comprising 80 per cent of the skull and 15 per cent of the body, is one of the most complete Torosaurus specimens found in Colorado.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2017-colorado-construction-workers-accidentally-dug-up-a-very-rare-dinosaur-fossil/articleshow/131243140.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2017-colorado-construction-workers-accidentally-dug-up-a-very-rare-dinosaur-fossil/articleshow/131243140.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T15:00:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131244218,imgsize-22210.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[In 2000, an amateur explorer found a hidden cave in France filled with ancient art and burials]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131243139.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A hidden cave in France's Dordogne region, Cussac Cave, revealed thousands of years of history when explorer Marc Delluc discovered detailed Upper Palaeolithic art.  Further exploration uncovered an intact human skeleton, suggesting the cave served as a prehistoric burial site and a place of worship.  Remarkably, ancient footprints preserved in the mud indicate the use of sophisticated footwear.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2000-an-amateur-explorer-found-a-hidden-cave-in-france-filled-with-ancient-art-and-burials/articleshow/131243139.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2000-an-amateur-explorer-found-a-hidden-cave-in-france-filled-with-ancient-art-and-burials/articleshow/131243139.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T14:30:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131243770,imgsize-418404.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[In 2002, cavers found a hidden skeleton that revealed an ancient Australian predator]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131243130.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Explorers found an ancient marsupial lion skeleton in a Nullarbor Plain cave. This discovery offers a unique look at extinct life. The cave's stable environment preserved the fossil for millions of years. Researchers are studying the skeleton to understand the predator's strength and hunting abilities. This find reveals a hidden world beneath the desert surface.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2002-cavers-found-a-hidden-skeleton-that-revealed-an-ancient-australian-predator/articleshow/131243130.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2002-cavers-found-a-hidden-skeleton-that-revealed-an-ancient-australian-predator/articleshow/131243130.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T14:08:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131243612,imgsize-114228.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[43-foot ‘marine T rex’ bigger than great white sharks and more brutal than any mosasaur discovered in Texas]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131259068.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/43-foot-marine-t-rex-bigger-than-great-white-sharks-and-more-brutal-than-any-mosasaur-discovered-in-texas/articleshow/131259068.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/43-foot-marine-t-rex-bigger-than-great-white-sharks-and-more-brutal-than-any-mosasaur-discovered-in-texas/articleshow/131259068.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T13:07:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131259188,imgsize-1534669.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Britain rolls out landmark transgender rules for single sex toilets, NHS wards and women-only spaces]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131258972.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Britain's new transgender access rules, following a Supreme Court ruling, allow single-sex spaces to exclude trans individuals if proportionate for privacy, safety, or dignity. This impacts healthcare, sports, and workplaces, sparking national debate on inclusion and rights. Organizations must balance protections, with case-by-case assessments encouraged.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-rolls-out-landmark-transgender-rules-for-single-sex-toilets-nhs-wards-and-women-only-spaces/articleshow/131258972.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-rolls-out-landmark-transgender-rules-for-single-sex-toilets-nhs-wards-and-women-only-spaces/articleshow/131258972.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T13:18:28+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131259295,imgsize-94234.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[New anti-Hindu hate monitor launched in UK amid rise in religious hate crimes]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131258779.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/new-anti-hindu-hate-monitor-launched-in-uk-amid-rise-in-religious-hate-crimes/articleshow/131258779.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/new-anti-hindu-hate-monitor-launched-in-uk-amid-rise-in-religious-hate-crimes/articleshow/131258779.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T13:18:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131259366,imgsize-864010.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[China just installed a giant floating wind turbine and it