ovation]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131256329.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/most-advanced-countries-in-the-world-ranked-from-south-koreas-high-digital-adoption-to-denmarks-pharmaceutical-innovation/articleshow/131256329.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/most-advanced-countries-in-the-world-ranked-from-south-koreas-high-digital-adoption-to-denmarks-pharmaceutical-innovation/articleshow/131256329.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T10:27:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131256571,imgsize-141832.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Greek philosopher Epicurus: “You don't develop courage by being happy in your relationships everyday. You develop it by…”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131255797.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-greek-philosopher-epicurus-you-dont-develop-courage-by-being-happy-in-your-relationships-everyday-you-develop-it-by/articleshow/131255797.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-greek-philosopher-epicurus-you-dont-develop-courage-by-being-happy-in-your-relationships-everyday-you-develop-it-by/articleshow/131255797.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T09:47:02+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131256137,imgsize-22114.cms"/></item><item><title><!